code: @Override protected JiraAccount createAccount(String name, Settings settings) {     return new JiraAccount(name, settings, httpClient). }
private static List<Setting<?>> getDynamicSettings() {     return Arrays.asList(SETTING_DEFAULT_ACCOUNT, SETTING_ALLOW_HTTP, SETTING_DEFAULTS). }
private static List<Setting<?>> getSecureSettings() {     return Arrays.asList(SETTING_SECURE_USER, SETTING_SECURE_PASSWORD, SETTING_SECURE_URL). }

public static List<Setting<?>> getSettings() {     List<Setting<?>> allSettings = new ArrayList<Setting<?>>(getDynamicSettings()).     allSettings.addAll(getSecureSettings()).     return allSettings. }
